sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>kserve-ingress-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/HF/OCI<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving (RawDeployment)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>VS: Forward request<br/>HTTP/80 (mesh-internal)
    VS->>KRBAC: Route to service<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS
    Note right of KRBAC: TokenReview +<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC->>Predictor: Authorized request<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    Predictor-->>KRBAC: Prediction response
    KRBAC-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,Storage: Model Loading (Init Container)
    Predictor->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS/GCS/HF credentials
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model artifacts

    participant GW2 as Gateway<br/>openshift-ai-inference<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as llm-d inference-scheduler<br/>ext_proc gRPC<br/>9002/TCP TLS
    participant Sidecar as routing-sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant VLLM as vLLM Container<br/>8001/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Client,VLLM: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService (Gateway API + llm-d)

    Client->>GW2: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    GW2->>EPP: ext_proc scheduling<br/>gRPC/9002 TLS (self-signed)<br/>mTLS
    Note right of EPP: InferencePool +<br/>InferenceModel routing
    EPP->>Sidecar: Route to selected pod<br/>HTTPS/8000 TLS (self-signed)
    Sidecar->>VLLM: Proxy to vLLM<br/>HTTPS/8001 TLS (self-signed)<br/>--enable-ssl-refresh
    VLLM-->>Sidecar: LLM Response
    Sidecar-->>EPP: Response
    EPP-->>GW2: Response
    GW2-->>Client: JSON Response

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Controller Reconciliation

    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Watch event<br/>(InferenceService/LLMInferenceService)
    K8sAPI-->>Gateway: Notify controller
    Note right of Gateway: kserve-controller-manager<br/>reconciles resources
    Gateway->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Note right of K8sAPI: Deployment, Service,<br/>HTTPRoute, VirtualService,<br/>InferencePool, InferenceModel,<br/>HPA, RBAC
